          <div class="cb-intro">
            <div class="cb-mark">The architectural endgame</div>
            <h3 class="cb-headline">One brain becomes <em>many</em>. <em>Many become</em> a nervous system.</h3>
            <p class="cb-lede">You start with one record domain. Customer master, supplier file, product catalog — wherever the business is most exposed. Once it's running, you add a second. By the time the third is in production, the brains are talking to each other. <b>What you've built is no longer a resolved record. It's the underlying language your business uses to decide things.</b></p>
